  "title": "Class 4 Delivery Driver #75627",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Class 4 Delivery Driver</strong></li><li>Working Location: Sungei Kadut</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Monday to Friday, 8am – 5pm, Sat 8am – 12pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Salary up to $3,000 + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive and operate a 24ft lorry, ensuring the safe and timely delivery of goods</li><li>Plan delivery routes efficiently to meet schedules and minimize delays.</li><li>Conduct daily vehicle checks and report any issues to ensure vehicles are in good working condition.</li><li>Complete delivery records, logbooks, and other paperwork accurately.</li><li>Adhere to all road safety, company, and regulatory guidelines during all deliveries.</li><li>Any other ad hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Driving License: Min. Class 4 & above</li><li>At least 2+ years of driving experience in Class 4 vehicles</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#75627 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
